{{Positionskarte~ |Welt (W3)|position= 2|lat= 50.45 |long= 30.5 |region=UA|wrap=manual|label=Kiew<br /><small>seit 1989</small>}}
{{Positionskarte~ |Welt (W3)|position= 4|lat=-17.825 |long= 31.05 |region=ZW|wrap=manual|label=Harare<br /><small>seit 1996</small>}}
